		{"id":"title","type":"text","text":"# LoreAI V2 Content Hub 架构图 v4","x":0,"y":-220,"width":600,"height":60,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"concept","type":"text","text":"**核心理念：** Canonical = Narrative（≈ core-narrative.json）。Blog 一步生成，Video 多三步（Planner → Script → Render），复杂度不同但同源。","x":-80,"y":-140,"width":760,"height":50},
		{"id":"a_src","type":"text","text":"**外部 Source**\n\n📄 Anthropic 官博\n📄 Influencer Blog\n🎬 YouTube 视频\n📄 Dev.to / Medium\n🐙 GitHub Release","x":-700,"y":40,"width":200,"height":240,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"a_s0","type":"text","text":"**Step 0: 内容提取**\n原文 → 结构化\n\n产出: `source_raw.md`","x":-420,"y":60,"width":220,"height":140,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"a_s05","type":"text","text":"**Step 0.5: 内容清洗**\nPDF/YT/Repo/Twitter\n各有专用 subagent\n\n产出: `source_blog.md`","x":-120,"y":60,"width":240,"height":140,"color":"2"},
