		{"id":"narrative","type":"text","text":"# 📦 Narrative（内容原子）\n\n≈ `core-narrative.json` 结构\n`story_spine`: background → breakthrough → mechanism → significance\n`key_points[]` / `faq[]` / `seo{}`\n**结构化分析，未格式化为任何媒介**","x":-280,"y":840,"width":640,"height":180,"color":"6"},
