		{"id":"b_research","type":"text","text":"**Gemini Deep Research**\n🔍 自动调研\n产出结构化报告","x":-420,"y":550,"width":240,"height":100,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"b_nargen","type":"text","text":"**Narrative 生成**\n\n产出: `core-narrative.json`\nstory_spine + key_points","x":-100,"y":550,"width":240,"height":100,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"insight","type":"text","text":"**⚡ 关键发现**\n\nDeep Research 的\n`core-narrative.json`\n和 blog2video 的\n`video_plan.json`\n**不是同一层级**\n\nNarrative = 分析层\nVideo Plan = 编辑策略层\nScript = 最终格式层","x":380,"y":1320,"width":280,"height":200,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"vid_plan","type":"text","text":"**Step 1: Video Planner**\n产出: `video_plan.json`\n\nhook_question / emotion_arc\nbomb_detail / 比喻方向 / 分集策略","x":-100,"y":1140,"width":380,"height":110,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"vid_script","type":"text","text":"**Step 2: Script Writer**\n产出: `video_N_script.md`\n\n中文口播脚本 + [SLIDE N: type] 标记\n~200字/分钟，为听觉优化","x":-100,"y":1290,"width":380,"height":110,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"vid_render","type":"text","text":"**Step 3+4: Slide → TTS → Render**\n→ `slide_N.html` → `.png` (Puppeteer)\n→ Edge TTS → `audio.mp3` + `.vtt`\n→ Remotion 合成 → `video_N.mp4`","x":-100,"y":1440,"width":380,"height":120,"color":"2"},
